{"word":"ἐκπαγλέομαι","slug":"ἐκπαγλέομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐκπαγλέομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be struck with amazement, to wonder greatly</i>, only in <a href='S:participle'>part.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to wonder at, admire exceedingly</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἔκπαγλος'><el>ἔκπαγλος</el></a>\n"}]}